Samizdat module for ruby 1.8
	
this module is usable outside of samizdat engine and provides following
classes:

 * antispam: simple wiki spam filter
 * cache: thread-safe time-limited fifo cache
 * sanitize: html validation (requires tidy)
 * storage: relational rdf storage (requires pg, mysql, or sqlite3 dbd driver)


this package contains samizdat module for ruby 1.8.